-- BrightSource Energy CEO Woolard Stepping Down, Mercury News Says
-- B y   J u s t i n   D o o m
-- 2013-06-06T21:41:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-06/brightsource-energy-ceo-woolard-stepping-down-mercury-news-says.html
John Woolard is stepping down as
chief executive officer of  BrightSource Energy Inc. (BRSE) , according
to the San Jose Mercury News.  His departure from the Oakland, California-based solar-thermal developer had been discussed for months, Woolard told
the newspaper. Executive Chairman David Ramm will serve as
interim CEO until a permanent replacement is found.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Doom in New York at 
 jdoom1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
